Iniciar Projeto 

yarn init -y 

yarn add react  
yarn add @babel/core @babel/cli @babel/preset-env -D
yarn add webpack webpack-cli webpack-dev-server -D
yarn add cross-env -D //Para definir variaveis ambientes independente do sistema
operacional.

yarn add @babel/preset-typescript -D
yarn add @types/react-dom

Arquivos para criar:

babel.config.js
webpack.config.js